verbose_text: The [Fgf8]/[pErk] dose response shows that Hs6st1 -/- tissue is de-sensitised to Fgf8 and saturating doses of Fgf8 only elicited ~ 60% of the pErk response of WT cultures after 1 and 2 h (compare XREF_FIG I to L).
evidence: Hs6st1 -/-  tissue is de-sensitised to Fgf8 and saturating doses of Fgf8 only elicited ~60% of the pErk
